Visualization,Description,Why it's useful
Sales Trend (Area Chart),Displays revenue over time (Monthly/Quarterly).,Helps identify peak seasons and growth patterns.
Top 5 Products (Bar Chart),Ranks products based on total sales volume.,Pinpoints high-performing inventory.
Regional Sales (Map),Shows bubble sizes based on sales in different regions.,Identifies geographic areas with the highest market share.
KPI Cards,"Shows Total Sales, Profit Margin, and Order Count.",Provides instant status of the business at a glance.
